<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>QUINT - Приватный софт для CS2</title>
    <style>
        /* Базовые настройки стиля */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0b0c10;
            color: #c5c6c7;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            width: 85%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Шапка сайта */
        header {
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2833;
            background-color: #0b0c10;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        header .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #66fcf1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #c5c6c7;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #66fcf1;
        }

        /* Главный экран (Hero) */
        .hero {
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.8), rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.9)), url('https://unsplash.com') no-repeat center center/cover;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: #66fcf1;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #45f3ff;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #66fcf1;
            color: #0b0c10;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(102, 252, 241, 0.6);
        }

        /* Блок Функций (Features) */
        .features {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background-color: #11141a;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .section-title span {
            color: #66fcf1;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #1f2833;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: border 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border: 1px solid #66fcf1;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #c5c6c7;
        }

        /* Тарифы / Скачивание */
        .pricing {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .price-card {
            background-color: #1f2833;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #66fcf1;
        }

        .price-card h2 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .cost {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #66fcf1;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .status {
            color: #2ecc71;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .status::before {
            content: '';
            display: inline-block;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background-color: #2ecc71;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* Подвал */
        footer {
            background-color: #0b0c10;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #1f2833;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Шапка сайта -->
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">QUINT Hack</div>
            <nav>
                <a href="#features">Функции</a>
                <a href="#download">Скачать</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Главная секция -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Доминируй в <span>Counter-Strike 2</span></h1>
            <p>Максимальная точность, удобная настройка и высокая оптимизация</p>
            <a href="#download" class="btn">Получить софт</a>
